OL,3,CChancellor to squeeze spending
OL,4,Cfollowing growth collapse
OL,6,FThe story of next week's spring
OL,7,Fstatement will be simple: there will
OL,8,Fbe lower economic growth in 2025, and
OL,9,Fprobably in 2026 too; and as a
OL,10,Fconsequence, there will be less money
OL,11,Favailable for public services for the
OL,12,Fspending review period 2026-2030.
OL,14,FHere are the bald numbers. The Office
OL,15,Ffor Budget Responsibility back in
OL,16,FOctober was forecasting growth this
OL,17,Fyear of 2%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
