OL,6,FSo on Wednesday the OBR's 2% will
OL,7,Fbecome circa 1%. I assume the
OL,8,Ffollowing year's 1.8% will also be
OL,9,Frevised down.
OL,11,FAnd lower growth means lower tax
OL,12,Frevenues.
OL,14,FThere's a double whammy that the
OL,15,Fgovernment's expected interest costs
OL,16,Fare also rising, by multiple billions
OL,17,Fof pounds per year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
