OL,3,CChancellor to squeeze spending
OL,4,Cfollowing growth collapse
OL,6,FSo what to do?
OL,8,FShe will not put up taxes. The widely
OL,9,Fcirculated notion that she will extend
OL,10,Fthe freeze on income tax allowances
OL,11,Ftill 2030 as a stealth tax will not be
OL,12,Fdeployed.
OL,14,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,15,FPolitics? Tom, Robert and Anushka dig
OL,16,Finto the biggest issues dominating the
OL,17,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,19,FThere will be zero tax changes next
OL,20,Fweek. It will be a borrowing and
OL,21,Fspending event.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
