OL,6,FBecause certain departments - defence,
OL,7,Fhealth, education - are guaranteed
OL,8,Fincreases greater than 1%, more or
OL,9,Fless forever.
OL,11,FSo the spending review that will
OL,12,Fdistribute this 1% between competing
OL,13,Fdepartments in June is a deeply
OL,14,Ffraught process.
OL,16,FWill it all be gloom from Reeves on
OL,17,Fhairshirt Wednesday?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
