OL,6,FAs I have been saying, Starmer's re-
OL,7,Farmament pledge is being fleshed out
OL,8,Finto a defence-centred industrial
OL,9,Finvestment and growth plan, the kernel
OL,10,Fof which you can see in Reeves's new
OL,11,F"steer" to the Labour's newly created
OL,12,FNational Wealth Fund.
OL,14,FSo all hope of economic recovery is
OL,15,Fnot lost, though it is a bit delayed.
